{"type": "article", "id": 2192, "title": "壁纸滚轮", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T20:35:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222249I9y7nRDJs1aGMhgK.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>复古风再度来袭，英国女孩 Clare Bosanquet 用油漆印花的方式替代壁纸，让你刷墙也能刷出新花样。不过，Clare 坦言这把神奇的印花油漆刷并不是她的独创发明，而是她去罗马尼亚时发现，当地的人几百年来一直用这种方法来装饰墙面。Clare 买回了滚轮，对传统的纹路和材质加以改良，大大丰富了印花的种类。手握一把滚轮，再加一把梯子，就可以动手刷墙了。定价 34.37 美元，</span><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/160497337/tussock-patterned-paint-roller?ref=listing-0\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a><span>。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222248yZsvSfqBF4QCd3nA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222248V4p6bDOwnBYUyc13.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5015625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}